To the people on this string.  I have never seen an uglier rock turned over in all the dialog that has gone by here.  I have gotten some mail from Doc Del and like him I will not go into what was said.  EXCEPT, who the fuck do you think you are attcaking a man's family?????  You assholes who personalize an issue by attacking those things that we love are as bad as those idiots who messed with us when we came home.<br>
Attack me, attack my beliefs, BUT LEAVE MY FAMILY out of it! Everyone has my e-mail address.  Come play , idiots..<br>
You people who use race as an excuse for your condition are as bad as McVeigh blowing up O.K. City because he was pissed at the gov't.<br>
Don't you guys get it?  If you tear apart and criticize those things that individually keeps us together, you destroy any hope of caring and understanding.<br>
Someone said that the vets are a culture ,  like a ethnic culture.  We have our own language, beliefs, and backgrounds. So don't savage one of our own because you disagree with him.  Especially, off line and personally where there is no support system.  Do it here and if you are out of line accept the consequences.  Dr. Spatz, in all his glory, posts and if he is wrong takes his hit.  Not like some of you small minded idiots.<br>
So, idiots, you want a piece of me!  Come get some!  But you better fix bayonets cause I intend to rip your fucking hearts out for what you low lifes did to one of us and someone I call my friend.  
